+<!ELEMENT unitPrefixes ( unitPrefix* ) >
+
+<!ELEMENT unitPrefix EMPTY >

+		<unitPrefix type='kibi' symbol='Ki' power2='10'> -->

+<!ATTLIST unitPrefix power2 NMTOKEN #IMPLIED >
+    <!--@MATCH:regex/[0-9]0-->
